Third-party algorithms adapted for the Password class and that ensure that they are using safe buffers internally when possible.

Common built-in crypt formats and algorithms used to retrieve concrete hashers.

Collections of popular formatted hashers.

Base and full implementations of passwords.
ml.alternet.security.web
Handle safe passwords on a Web environment, meaning that in the Web processing chain, a password NEVER appear as a String (unsafe) inside the Web container.
ml.alternet.security.web.jetty
Handle safe passwords inside the Jetty Web server, meaning that in the Web processing chain, a password NEVER appear as a String (unsafe) inside the Jetty server.
ml.alternet.security.web.jetty.auth
Authentication support in Jetty.
ml.alternet.security.web.server
Helper classes for Web containers such as Jetty, Tomcat...
ml.alternet.security.web.tomcat
